# Auto detect text files and perform LF normalization
# see https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/remote/troubleshooting#_resolving-git-line-ending-issues-in-wsl-resulting-in-many-modified-files
# see https://stackoverflow.com/questions/21822650/disable-git-eol-conversions
* text=false
*.{cmd,[cC][mM][dD]} text eol=crlf
*.{bat,[bB][aA][tT]} text eol=crlf
# scripts should be LF
*.sh eol=lf 
manager eof=lf
manager-bak=lf
